  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "7 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd  \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b86\u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A 7-year-old boy was stabbed with a sharp weapon",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 7-year-old boy was stabbed with a sharp weapon and is undergoing treatment at Badulla Hospital with massive injuries.",
        "A boy who went to the shop to buy a mobile phone recharge card for his father was attacked.",
        "The incident took place yesterday (31) around 6 o'clock in the evening, and the boy from the village of Kandhaketiya-Kalugahagadura has been admitted to the hospital with injuries.",
        "It is reported that a 50-member team including five medical specialists has performed surgery on the boy and the boy is currently undergoing treatment in the intensive care unit.",
        "Commenting on the incident, the boy's father said that he handed the boy 100 rupees and told him to buy a refill card.",
        "The road leading to the shop is very small. He told us that there are forests on both sides and his son shouted within 5 minutes of going to the shop.",
        "He said that then he observed that a person who used to visit his house ran away from there.",
        "The father said that the suspect came to the house before his son went to the shop and when he asked the suspect to drink tea he refused and left the betel nut.",
        "Later, the injured son was taken to Meekahakivula Hospital. From there we took him to Badula General Hospital.",
        "The Padula police said that investigations have been started to arrest the 51-year-old suspect."
      ],
